<p>
<note n="0419001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0419001">〔大〕－【明】，〔大宋〕－【宮】</note>
<note n="0419002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0419002">〔臣〕－【明】＊</note>
<note n="0419003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0419003">猶＝由【元】【明】</note>
